data.eml:eml: Speleonectes williamsi, a new species of Remipedia (Crustacea) from the Bahamas

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Hartke, Tamara R., Koenemann, Stefan, Yager, Jill (2011): Speleonectes williamsi, a new species of Remipedia (Crustacea) from the Bahamas. Zootaxa 3115: 21-28, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.206642
